sentences: Bailey Thomas Cabello May (born 6 August 2002) is a Filipino-British actor, model, singer, and television personality.
Bailey Thomas Cabello May (born 6 August 2002) is a Filipino-British actor, model, singer, and television personality.
In 2015, he successfully auditioned for the 10th year edition of Pinoy Big Brother titled  Pinoy Big Brother: 737, and eventually placed as the third runner-up (4th Teen Big Placer).
